OL,3,CStrong aftershocks rattle Venezuela as
OL,4,Crescue teams race to find more
OL,5,Csurvivors
OL,7,FHopes of finding more survivors days
OL,8,Fafter two powerful earthquakes struck
OL,9,FVenezuela are fading by the hour as
OL,10,Faftershocks continue to shake the
OL,11,Fcountry.
OL,13,FAt least 1,450 people have been killed
OL,14,Fand as many as 50,000 have been
OL,15,Freported missing, say authorities amid
OL,16,Fgrowing criticism the government's
OL,17,Fresponse was inadequate.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
