OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782749903
OL,3,CStrong aftershocks rattle Venezuela as
OL,4,Crescue teams race to find more
OL,5,Csurvivors
OL,7,FEven as the likelihood of finding
OL,8,Fpeople alive diminished, local and
OL,9,Finternational rescuers continued to
OL,10,Fpull survivors from the rubble of
OL,11,Fcollapsed buildings, offering
OL,12,Fanguished families a sliver of hope.
OL,14,FTwo 11-year-old boys were found alive
OL,15,Fseparately in La Guaira, one of the
OL,16,Fhardest-hit states, and in the town of
OL,17,FCaraballeda.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
