OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782749903
OL,3,CStrong aftershocks rattle Venezuela as
OL,4,Crescue teams race to find more
OL,5,Csurvivors
OL,7,FVenezuela's Interim President Delcy
OL,8,FRodriguez said over 2,600 rescue
OL,9,Fworkers from Mexico, Spain, Qatar, the
OL,10,FUS and UK had arrived with trained
OL,11,Fsearch dogs and machinery.
OL,13,FDespite the "most brutal natural
OL,14,Fcatastrophe" in Venezuela's history,
OL,15,Fshe said: "We always maintain hope."
OL,17,FThe first 48 to 72 hours after a
OL,18,Fnatural disaster are crucial to rescue
OL,19,Fefforts, though survival can be
OL,20,Fextended if people have access to food
OL,21,Fand water.
