OL,3,CStrong aftershocks rattle Venezuela as
OL,4,Crescue teams race to find more
OL,5,Csurvivors
OL,7,FThe magnitude 7.2 and 7.5 quakes last
OL,8,Fweek left a trail of devastation and
OL,9,Fcaused more than 770 buildings to
OL,10,Fcollapse, leaving many trapped inside.
OL,12,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FThe United Nations said up to 6.8
OL,18,Fmillion of Venezuela's nearly 30
OL,19,Fmillion residents may be affected.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
