OL,3,CStrong aftershocks rattle Venezuela as
OL,4,Crescue teams race to find more
OL,5,Csurvivors
OL,7,FA layer of dust coated coastal
OL,8,Fcommunities, and as the stench of
OL,9,Fdecomposing bodies spread, more people
OL,10,Fbegan to wear masks.
OL,12,FThe risk of further damage remains as
OL,13,Faftershocks measuring 4.2 and 4.5 hit
OL,14,Fthe nation.
OL,16,FRodruigez shared a video of a young
OL,17,Fman named Aaron Levi Cantillo, who was
OL,18,Fpulled out of the rubble after being
OL,19,Ftrapped for 106 hours
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
