OL,3,CStrong aftershocks rattle Venezuela as
OL,4,Crescue teams race to find more
OL,5,Csurvivors
OL,7,FAn 11-year-old boy, named Moises, was
OL,8,Fpulled from under about 3m (9.8ft) of
OL,9,Fdebris.
OL,11,FA Colombian rescuer was reportedly
OL,12,Foverheard on a walkie-talkie saying
OL,13,Fthe young boy was found near his
OL,14,Fsister and mother, who had both died.
OL,16,FCrowds gathered when rescue crews from
OL,17,Fthe US, France and Venezuela hauled a
OL,18,Fman and his son from a crack in the
OL,19,Fconcrete, covered in dust and almost
OL,20,Funresponsive.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
