OL,3,CStrong aftershocks rattle Venezuela as
OL,4,Crescue teams race to find more
OL,5,Csurvivors
OL,7,FHelmet-clad teams pulled them on a
OL,8,Fblack tarp and passed the two
OL,9,Fcarefully through the crowd to an
OL,10,Fambulance to hydrate them through an
OL,11,FIV.
OL,13,FOnlookers burst into applause in a
OL,14,Fmoment of relief, then rescuers
OL,15,Fcontinued working.
OL,17,FAuthorities said they had treated more
OL,18,Fthan 3,100 wounded people, including
OL,19,Fmany with crush injuries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
