OL,3,CStrong aftershocks rattle Venezuela as
OL,4,Crescue teams race to find more
OL,5,Csurvivors
OL,7,FThe disaster poses a significant
OL,8,Fchallenge for Rodriguez, the former
OL,9,Fvice president who took office in
OL,10,FJanuary after the US capture and
OL,11,Fsubsequent removal of Nicolas Maduro.
OL,13,FSince then, Washington has played an
OL,14,Fincreasingly powerful role in
OL,15,Fdictating the future of the South
OL,16,FAmerican nation.
OL,18,FVenezuela faced economic disarray for
OL,19,Fmore than a decade and many people
OL,20,Freject the legitimacy of the political
OL,21,Fmovement Rodriguez represents.
